result.title: Welcome to acmASCIS level 2 training'18.
result.content:
Hello there,

Congratulations on making it to level #2 training, We are looking forward to seeing you.

In order to make our communications easier, we need you to send us a message with the following:

1) A link to your Facebook account.

2) Your active e-mail.

3) A drive link with view access contains a schedule of your group.

4) Your section.

Please send this information as soon as possible, further updates about level #2 will be shared with you on the facebook group as soon as possible so don't bother asking about anything yet.

Good luck.
